ants:**\n- `IdentitySecretName = \"picod-router-identity\"`\n- `PublicKeyDataKey = \"public.pem\"`\n- `DefaultSandboxTTL = 8` (hours)\n- `DefaultSandboxIdleTimeout = 15` (minutes)\n\n**Timing/Scan Constants:**\n- `DefaultIdleTimeout = 15 * time.Minute`\n- `MaxOrphanScanLimit = 100`\n\n**GC Cleanup Reason Constants:**\n- `GRCleanupReasonTTLExpired = \"ttl_expired\"`\n- `GRCleanupReasonIdle = \"idle\"`\n- `GRCleanupReasonOrphanCR = \"orphan_cr\"`\n- `GRCleanupReasonGhostEntry = \"ghost_entry\"`\n\n### File: `models.go`\n\n**Interface: `MetricsRecorder`**\n```go\ntype MetricsRecorder interface {\n    IncReconcileTotal(resourceType string, result string)\n    ObserveReconcileDuration(resourceType string, duration time.Duration)\n    IncReconcileErrors(resourceType string, errorType string)\n    SetWorkqueueDepth(depth int)\n    IncWorkqueueAdds(resourceType string)\n    IncGCCleanupTotal(reason string)\n    ObserveGCCleanupDuration(reason string, duration time.Duration)\n    IncGCCleanupErrors(reason string)\n    ObserveGCCycleDuration(duration time.Duration)\n}\n```\n\n**Struct: `CreateSandboxRequest`**\n- Fields: `Kind`, `Name`, `Namespace` (all string, JSON-tagged)\n- Method: `Validate() error`\n\n**Struct: `CreateSandboxResponse`**\n- Fields: `SessionID`, `SandboxID`, `SandboxName` (string), `EntryPoints` ([]EntryPoint)\n\n**Struct: `EntryPoint`**\n- Fields: `Path`, `Protocol`, `Endpoint` (all string)\n\n**Struct: `SandboxInfo`**\n- Fields: `SessionID`, `SandboxName`, `SandboxID`, `WorkloadName`, `Namespace`, `Kind`, `PodIP`, `EntryPoints`, `CreatedAt`, `ExpiresAt`, `Status`, `LastActivityAt`\n\n**Struct: `SandboxStatus`**\n- Fields: `Status` (string), `Error` (error)\n\n### File: `sandbox_create.go`\n\n**Interface: `Store`**\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, info *SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *SandboxInfo) error\n    GetSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*SandboxInfo, error)\n    DeleteSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n    ListSandboxes(ctx context.Context) ([]*SandboxInfo, error)\n}\n```\n\n**Interface: `SandboxReconcilerWatcher`**\n```go\ntype SandboxReconcilerWatcher interface {\n    WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, name string) (<-chan SandboxStatus, error)\n}\n```\n\n**Interface: `TokenCache`**\n```go\ntype TokenCache interface {\n    GetOrCreateUserK8sClient(namespace, saName, token string) (dynamic.Interface, error)\n}\n```\n\n**Interface: `UserClientFactory`**\n```go\ntype UserClientFactory interface {\n    CreateUserClient(token string) (dynamic.Interface, error)\n}\n```\n\n**Struct: `SandboxCreateHandlerDeps`** (dependency injection struct)\n- Fields: `DynamicClient`, `Clientset`, `KubeClientset`, `InformerFactory`, `Store`, `Reconciler`, `TokenCache`, `UserClientFactory`, `EnableAuth`\n\n**Struct: `SandboxCreateHandler`**\n- Constructor: `NewSandboxCreateHandler(deps *SandboxCreateHandlerDeps) *SandboxCreateHandler`\n- Methods:\n  - `getDynamicClient(c *gin.Context) (dynamic.Interface, error)`\n  - `CreateAgentRuntimeSandbox(c *gin.Context)`\n  - `CreateCodeInterpreterSandbox(c *gin.Context)`\n  - `rollbackCR(ctx context.Context, gvr schema.GroupVersionResource, namespace, name string, dynClient dynamic.Interface) error`\n  - `buildAgentRuntimeSandboxCR(template *runtimev1alpha1.AgentRuntime, sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace string) (*unstructured.Unstructured, error)`\n  - `buildCodeInterpreterSandboxCR(template *runtimev1alpha1.CodeInterpreter, sessionID, sandboxName, workloadName, namespace string, ports []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort) (*unstructured.Unstructured, string, error)`\n  - `injectPicodAuthEnv(cr *unstructured.Unstructured, namespace string, clientset kubernetes.Interface) error`\n  - `resolvePodIP(ctx context.Context, sandboxName, namespace string, sandboxCR *unstructured.Unstructured, clientset kubernetes.Interface) (string, error)`\n  - `buildEntryPoints(podIP string, ports []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort) []EntryPoint`\n\n**Package-level functions:**\n- `generateSessionID() string`\n- `generateSandboxName(workloadName string) string`\n- `RandString(n int) string`\n- `getPortsOrDefaults(ports []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort) []runtimev1alpha1.TargetPort`\n\n### File: `sandbox_delete.go`\n\n**Struct: `SandboxDeleteHandlerDeps`**\n- Fields: `DynamicClient`, `Clientset`, `InformerFactory`, `Store`, `EnableAuth`, `TokenCache`\n\n**Struct: `SandboxDeleteHandler`**\n- Constructor: `NewSandboxDeleteHandler(deps *SandboxDeleteHandlerDeps) *SandboxDeleteHandler`\n- Methods:\n  - `getDynamicClient(c *gin.Context) (dynamic.Interface, error)`\n  - `DeleteSandbox(c *gin.Context)`\n  - `DeleteSandboxByName(c *gin.Context)`\n  - `resolveGVR(kind string) (schema.GroupVersionResource, error)`\n\n**Struct: `DeleteSandboxRequest`**\n- Fields: `SessionID`, `Namespace` (string)\n- Method: `Validate() error`\n\n**Struct: `DeleteSandboxResponse`**\n- Fields: `SessionID`, `SandboxName`, `Deleted` (bool), `Message` (string, omitempty)\n\n### File: `sandbox_lifecycle.go`\n\n**Struct: `LifecycleManagerDeps`**\n- Fields: `DynamicClient`, `Store`, `CheckInterval`, `DefaultTTL`, `DefaultIdleTimeout`, `MetricsRecorder`\n\n**Struct: `LifecycleManager`**\n- Constructor: `NewLifecycleManager(deps *LifecycleManagerDeps) *LifecycleManager`\n- Methods:\n  - `Start(ctx context.Context)`\n  - `Stop()`\n  - `runCleanupLoop(ctx context.Context)`\n  - `runGCCycle(ctx context.Context)`\n  - `cleanupExpiredSandboxes(ctx context.Context) (int, int, error)`\n  - `isExpired(info *SandboxInfo, now time.Time) bool`\n  - `isIdleExpired(info *SandboxInfo, idleTimeout time.Duration, now time.Time) bool`\n  - `deleteSandbox(ctx context.Context, info *SandboxInfo, reason string) error`\n  - `cleanupOrphanCRs(ctx context.Context) (int, error)`\n  - `cleanupGhostEntries(ctx context.Context) (int, error)`\n  - `resolveGVR(kind string) (schema.GroupVersionResource, error)`\n  - `calculateTimeToIdle(info *SandboxInfo, now time.Time) *time.Duration`\n  - `GetSandboxStatus(c *gin.Context)`\n  - `ListSandboxes(c *gin.Context)`\n  - `ExtendSandboxTTL(c *gin.Context)`\n\n**Struct: `SandboxStatusResponse`**\n- Fields: `SessionID`, `SandboxName`, `SandboxID`, `Status`, `CreatedAt`, `ExpiresAt`, `LastActivityAt`, `TimeToExpiry` (*time.Duration), `TimeToIdle` (*time.Duration), `IsExpired` (bool), `IsIdle` (bool), `EntryPoints` ([]EntryPoint)\n\n**Struct: `SandboxListItem`**\n- Fields: `SessionID`, `SandboxName`, `WorkloadName`, `Namespace`, `Kind`, `Status`, `CreatedAt`, `ExpiresAt`, `LastActivityAt`, `TimeToExpiry` (*time.Duration), `TimeToIdle` (*time.Duration), `IsExpired` (bool), `IsIdle` (bool)\n\n**Struct: `ListSandboxesResponse`**\n- Fields: `Total` (int), `Items` ([]SandboxListItem)\n\n**Struct: `ExtendTTLRequest`**\n- Fields: `ExtensionDuration` (time.Duration)\n- Method: `Validate() error`\n\n**Struct: `ExtendTTLResponse`**\n- Fields: `SessionID` (string), `NewExpiry` (time.Time)\n\n**Package-level functions:**\n- `parseIdleTimeoutFromAnnotations(annotations map[string]string, defaultTimeout time.Duration) time.Duration`\n- `extractIdleTimeoutFromCR(cr *unstructured.Unstructured, defaultTimeout time.Duration) time.Duration`\n\n---\n\n## Package: `reconciler`\n\n### File: `types.go`\n\n**Constants:**\n- Resource types: `resourceTypeAgentRuntime`, `resourceTypeCodeInterpreter`, `resourceTypePod`\n- Results: `resultSuccess`, `resultError`\n- Error types: `errorTypeStoreUnreachable`, `errorTypeListerFailure`, `errorTypeInvalidData`, `errorTypeUpdateFailed`\n- Conditions: `ConditionReady = \"Ready\"`, `ReasonTerminated = \"Terminated\"`\n- Tuning: `maxRetries = 15`, `defaultWorkers = 2`, `cacheSyncTimeout = 30s`, `shutdownTimeout = 30s`\n- Status: `StatusPending`, `StatusRunning`, `StatusTerminated`\n\n**Interface: `Store`** (reconciler-specific, differs from handler's Store)\n```go\ntype Store interface {\n    StoreSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *handler.SandboxInfo) error\n    UpdateSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string, info *handler.SandboxInfo) error\n    DeleteSandboxBySessionID(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) error\n    GetSandbox(ctx context.Context, sessionID string) (*handler.SandboxInfo, error)\n    ListSandboxes(ctx context.Context) (map[string]*handler.SandboxInfo, error)\n}\n```\n\n**Struct: `ReconcilerDeps`**\n- Fields: `Clientset`, `InformerFactory`, `ARLister`, `CILister`, `PodInformer`, `Store`, `Workers` (int), `MetricsRecorder`\n\n### File: `reconciler.go`\n\n**Struct: `SandboxReconciler`**\n- Fields: `clientset`, `informerFactory`, `arLister`, `ciLister`, `podInformer`, `store`, `workqueue`, `workers`, `metricsRecorder`, `mu`, `running`, `stopCh`\n- Constructor: `NewSandboxReconciler(deps ReconcilerDeps) *SandboxReconciler`\n- Methods:\n  - `registerEventHandlers()`\n  - `Enqueue(namespace, name string)`\n  - `Run(stopCh <-chan struct{})`\n  - `WatchSandboxOnce(namespace, name string) (<-chan handler.SandboxStatus, error)`\n\n### File: `agentruntime.go`\n\n**Functions:**\n- `mapConditionToStatus(conditions []metav1.Condition) string`\n- `(r *SandboxReconciler) reconcileAgentRuntime(key string) error`\n- `isNotFoundError(err error) bool`\n\n### File: `codeinterpreter.go`\n\n**Functions:**\n- `(r *SandboxReconciler) reconcileCodeInterpreter(key string) error`\n\n### File: `event_handlers.go`\n\n**Functions (all on `*SandboxReconciler`):**\n- `onAgentRuntimeAdd(obj interface{})`\n- `onAgentRuntimeUpdate(oldObj, newObj interface{})`\n- `onAgentRuntimeDelete(obj interface{})`\n- `onCodeInterpreterAdd(obj interface{})`\n- `onCodeInterpreterUpdate(oldObj, newObj interface{})`\n- `onCodeInterpreterDelete(obj interface{})`\n- `onPodAdd(obj interface{})`\n- `onPodUpdate(oldObj, newObj interface{})`\n- `onPodDelete(obj interface{})`\n\n### File: `pod.go`\n\n**Functions:**\n- `(r *SandboxReconciler) reconcilePod(key string) error`\n- `buildEntryPointsFromSandboxInfo(info *handler.SandboxInfo, podIP string) []handler.EntryPoint`\n- `extractPort(endpoint string) string`\n\n### File: `sync.go`\n\n**Functions (all on `*SandboxReconciler`):**\n- `syncHandler(key string) error`\n- `processNextWorkItem() bool`\n- `runWorker()`\n- `determineResourceType(key string) string`\n\n### File: `metrics.go`\n\n**Struct: `PrometheusMetricsRecorder`**\n- Fields: `reconcileTotal`, `reconcileDuration`, `reconcileErrors`, `workqueueDepth`, `workqueueAdds`, `gcCleanupTotal`, `gcCleanupDuration`, `gcCleanupErrors`, `gcCycleDuration` (all Prometheus metric types)\n- Constructor: `NewPrometheusMetricsRecorder(reg prometheus.Registerer) *PrometheusMetricsRecorder`\n- Methods (implements `handler.MetricsRecorder`):\n  - `IncReconcileTotal(resourceType string, result string)`\n  - `ObserveReconcileDuration(resourceType string, duration time.Duration)`\n  - `IncReconcileErrors(resourceType string, errorType string)`\n  - `SetWorkqueueDepth(depth int)`\n  - `IncWorkqueueAdds(resourceType string)`\n  - `IncGCCleanupTotal(reason string)`\n  - `ObserveGCCleanupDuration(reason string, duration time.Duration)`\n  - `IncGCCleanupErrors(reason string)`\n  - `ObserveGCCycleDuration(duration time.Duration)`\n\n---\n\n## Package: `response`\n\n### File: `response.go`\n\n**Struct: `SuccessResponse`**\n- Fields: `Data` (interface{}), `Message` (string, omitempty)\n\n**Struct: `ErrorResponse`**\n- Fields: `Error` (string), `Code` (int), `RequestID` (string, omitempty)\n\n**Functions:**\n- `JSON(c *gin.Context, code int, data interface{})`\n- `Created(c *gin.Context, data interface{})`\n- `Error(c *gin.Context, httpCode int, code int, message string)`\n- `ErrorWithID(c *gin.Context, httpCode int, code int, message string, requestID string)`\n\n---\n\n## All Dependencies Imported\n\n### External (third-party):\n| Import | Used In |\n|--------|---------|\n| `github.com/gin-gonic/gin` | handler (create, delete, lifecycle), response |\n| `github.com/google/uuid` | handler/sandbox_create.go |\n| `github.com/prometheus/client_golang/prometheus` | reconciler/metrics.go, reconciler/metrics_test.go |\n| `github.com/stretchr/testify/assert` | All test files |\n| `github.com/stretchr/testify/require` | All test files |\n\n### Kubernetes:\n| Import | Used In |\n|--------|---------|\n| `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | handler/sandbox_create.go, reconciler/event_handlers.go, reconciler/pod.go |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/api/errors` | handler (create, delete, lifecycle), reconciler (agentruntime, codeinterpreter, pod, sync) |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | handler (create, delete, lifecycle), reconciler (agentruntime) |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1/unstructured` | handler (create, lifecycle) |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/labels` | handler/sandbox_create.go |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime` | handler/sandbox_create.go, handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | handler (constants, create, delete, lifecycle) |\n| `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/util/runtime` | reconciler/sync.go |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic` | handler (create, delete, lifecycle) |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/dynamic/fake` | handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/informers` | handler/sandbox_delete.go |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/informers/core/v1` | reconciler (types, reconciler) |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/kubernetes` | handler/sandbox_create.go |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/tools/cache` | reconciler (reconciler, agentruntime, codeinterpreter, event_handlers, pod, sync) |\n| `k8s.io/client-go/util/workqueue` | reconciler/reconciler.go |\n\n### Internal (agentcube project):\n| Import | Used In |\n|--------|---------|\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset` | handler (create, delete), reconciler (types, reconciler) |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/informers/externalversions` | handler/sandbox_create.go, reconciler (types, reconciler) |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/listers/runtime/v1alpha1` | reconciler (types, reconciler) |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | handler/sandbox_create.go |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/handler` | reconciler (types, agentruntime, codeinterpreter, pod) |\n| `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/workloadmanager/response` | handler (create, delete, lifecycle), handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go |\n\n---\n\n## Existing Test Files\n\n| Test File | Location | Test Count (approx) |\n|-----------|----------|---------------------|\n| `sandbox_delete_test.go` | handler/ | ~20 tests |\n| `sandbox_lifecycle_test.go` | handler/ | ~26 tests |\n| `metrics_test.go` | reconciler/ | ~7 tests |\n| `response_test.go` | response/ | ~6 tests |\n\n**Test coverage areas:**\n- **handler/sandbox_delete_test.go**: `DeleteSandboxRequest.Validate`, `SandboxDeleteHandler.resolveGVR`, `DeleteSandbox` handler (invalid body, missing sessionID, session not found), `DeleteSandboxByName` handler (missing name, missing namespace), JSON serialization of responses, `mockStore` CRUD operations, `SandboxInfo` field tests\n- **handler/sandbox_lifecycle_test.go**: `LifecycleManager` construction (defaults, custom values), `isExpired` (with ExpiresAt, with CreatedAt, no timestamps, boundary conditions), `Start/Stop` idempotency, `ExtendTTLRequest.Validate`, `GetSandboxStatus` (missing sessionID, not found, success), `ListSandboxes` (empty, with items, filter by namespace, filter by status), `ExtendSandboxTTL` (missing sessionID, invalid body, session not found, expired sandbox, success), JSON serialization of all response types, `cleanupExpiredSandboxes` integration\n- **reconciler/metrics_test.go**: `PrometheusMetricsRecorder` GC methods, nil receiver safety for all methods, Prometheus metric registration verification\n- **response/response_test.go**: `JSON` success, `Created` success, `Error` (BadRequest, NotFound, Internal), `ErrorWithID`\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_284e96b07ffeaMWQKO6ke8Do06","mode